(82,'ANTH',4900,'Honours Anthropology Thesis I',0.50,'Development and design of an honours thesis proposal conducted under the supervision of a faculty member. Recommended to honours major students.','Department of Sociology and Anthropology','Guelph','15.00 credits including ANTH*3690, (SOAN*3070 or SOAN*3120)',98,15.00),
